{"tid":927983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講個笑話俾大家知","createTime":"2018-12-04T13:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T14:05:18.000Z","uid":37528,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4cba7872e636e3af59addd7f601198d98f2d4472","tid":927983,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支那</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中美達成暫時不互徵新關稅共識。在北京，中國人民大學國際關係學院副院長金燦榮表示，預計中美貿易磨擦，到明年年中將告一段落，但以後仍可能經常出現。<br />\n<br />\n金燦榮說，中美元首近日就貿易問題會面，較兩國高層外交好一些，不過貿易問題只屬休戰，相信90天的談判過程將會很艱難，但仍比雙方隔空威脅好。<br />\n<br />\n金燦榮說到明年中，雙方貿易磨擦的代價就會較為明顯，屆時都會有較大的政治意願，處理有關問題。他說<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國當局近日提出擴大需求，相信中國經濟在明年年中較現時好，而美國在總統特朗普管治下，美國經濟將轉差，有可能導致美國在談判上改變不理智及高要求的情況</span></span>。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n金燦榮表示，美國拒絕承認中國掘起，並視中國為競爭者，相信中美之間將由以往競爭與合作的「五五比」，改變為「七三比」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCOB459.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCOB459.jpg&h=68daf3b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXp9FEv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXp9FEv.gif&h=4e31732b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xZYeRMb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxZYeRMb.png&h=42630fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41d125a47bcb9ab9c20a0e17c474f909d9884f24","tid":927983,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5iB5bp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5iB5bp.png&h=e0ced9c4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}